      "text": "It was old maids so they don't rape them, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, they do the dirt in the house, and-- you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just we got lucky they was nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the reason I can't-- I cannot say I hate Germans, what they did for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
